    "For now, let us turn to explore more concrete theses that CCC can ground, focusing first on a comparison of human users and GenAI systems.",
    "Users vs. GenAI: a spectrum of creatorshipCan GenAI systems be part of co-creating collectives?",
    "CCC suggests yes, for they may exhibit a number of important features and to significant enough degrees to merit candidacy.",
    "But how would credit for an output be allocated between users and GenAI systems?",
